  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04 triggered)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is 3. Twelve of the thirteen credibility factors have been assessed; the Equivalency of input parameters factor is recorded as not-assessed on the basis that the assessment team judged it inapplicable to this COU because the validation experiment uses the same pump geometry and boundary conditions as the clinical model. However, the team did not encode this judgment as factorStatus 'not-applicable' — it remains 'not-assessed' — leaving a material epistemic gap at MRL 3. Decision: Accepted.",
